---
---

<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
    <div class="fun-card border-4 border-purple-400 border-opacity-30 bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-purple-50">
      <div class="text-5xl mb-4">🏫</div>
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-pink-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-4">
        About Our Academy
      </h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        The course is located in <strong>Our Lady's Secondary School, Terenure</strong> with easy access by bus and free car parking.
      </p>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-2xl">👩‍🏫</span>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Run by qualified Home Economics teachers with lots of teaching experience</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-2xl">👫</span>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Maximum 20 students per class</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-2xl">🍳</span>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Well-equipped cookery kitchens</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-2xl">🏠</span>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Each student cooks 2 dishes each day to bring home!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="fun-card border-4 border-orange-400 border-opacity-30 bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-orange-50">
      <div class="text-5xl mb-4">🎯</div>
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-pink-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-4">
        What You'll Learn
      </h3>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-2xl">⚖️</span>
          <p class="text-gray-600"><strong>Weighing & Measuring:</strong> Essential cooking skills</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-2xl">🥗</span>
          <p class="text-gray-600"><strong>Healthy Eating:</strong> Learn about nutrition and wholesome foods</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-2xl">🍽️</span>
          <p class="text-gray-600"><strong>Classic Dishes:</strong> Master both savoury and sweet recipes</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-2xl">⏰</span>
          <p class="text-gray-600"><strong>Life Skills:</strong> Time management and organization</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-2xl">🎉</span>
          <p class="text-gray-600"><strong>Confidence:</strong> Build self-esteem through achievement</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-8 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg text-center" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fbbf24 0%, #f97316 100%);">
    <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-3 text-white">
      📞 Ready to Join?
    </h3>
    <p class="text-xl mb-4 text-white">
      Book your place today with a €50 deposit!
    </p>
    <a href="#contact" class="inline-block bg-white text-orange-500 font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-full hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-200 shadow-xl">
      Contact Us Now! 🚀
    </a>
  </div>
</div>
